<p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;"><img alt="The payment methods accepted are cash, checks, money orders, electronic checks, and MasterCard credit cards." height="204" src="Images/financial-services/111101_purchasecard_17.jpg" style="float: right;" title="Payment Methods" width="350" />The Bursar’s Office accepts cash, checks, money orders, electronic checks (E-Checks), and all major credit cards except VISA.</p>
<br />
<p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">PLEASE NOTE: All major credit cards <strong>except VISA</strong> are accepted<strong>.</strong></p>
