<hr style="color: #fff; background-color: #fff; border: 1px dotted gray; border-style: none none dotted;" />
<p style="font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">E-Check – No Service Charge<br />All Major Credit Cards (Except VISA) – 2.75% Service Charge</p>
<ul style="list-style-type: circle; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
<li>Online at <a href="http://my.byui.edu">my.byui.edu</a> <span style="font-size: smaller;">(For more information about updated Personal Account information click <a href="x42140.xml" title="CASHNet">here</a>)</span>.</li>
</ul>
<h4 style="font-weight: bold;">Cash Payments</h4>
<hr style="color: #fff; background-color: #fff; border: 1px dotted gray; border-style: none none dotted;" />
<ul style="list-style-type: circle; font-family: Verdana, Arial, sans-serif;">
